data.text: @ouinne Weird dang trophy. That, uh, let’s go gazelle? has a malfunctioning face! I’d want another head, myself, one with less horn-coming-out-of-its-sinuses-ness. As it is, I’d literally always tell people “look at my dead animal. don’t worry, those horns aren’t made of boogers.”
This is really why  I bought it -the pics! This weird trophy head hung in the army and navy club. https://t.co/pvqxk5wpyX
